<episodedetails><title>Joan Rivers: A Piece of Work</title><plot>Joan Rivers: A Piece of Work takes the audience on a year-long ride with Joan Rivers in her 76th year of life; it peels away the mask of an iconic comedian, laying bare both the struggle and thrill of living life as a groundbreaking female performer.</plot></episodedetails>